<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fire has varied impacts on this alliance from reduction in cover of <i>Cylindropuntia acanthocarpa </i> to increase in cover of disturbance-tolerant plants such as <i>Acamptopappus sphaerocephalus, Ericameria cooperi, </i>and <i>Pleuraphis rigida</i>. However, the fire characteristics are not well-known for this alliance. Other disturbances, such as grazing, enable these species to increase.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
